<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-BBN-DODGERS-WRITETHRU-LADN </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
PADRES BEAT DODGERS
</HEADLINE>
 (For use by NYTimes News Service clients) 
CORRECTS GIANTS-ROCKIES SERIES IN FOURTH GRAF 
By MATT McHALE  
 c.1998 Los Angeles Daily News  
<TEXT>
<P>
   LOS ANGELES _ Two steps forward, two steps back looks more and
more like the Dodgers' dance of doom.
</P>
<P>
   After winning the first two games in their series with
first-place San Diego, they finished with a split Sunday after Ken
