<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1998-07-13 13:25 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A2223 &Cx1f; tdt-z
u a &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-SCI-AIDS-FUTURE-BOS &LR;      07-13 1399
