Rules'' is an epic-sized slice of theater _ six hours' worth, plus
a dinner break. If theater-going were the same as weight-training,
the Taper would be this summer's answer to Muscle Beach. By Reed
Johnson. 
. 
MOVIE-GAMES (Los Angeles) _ As sure as that big avalanche swept
away the Huns in ``Mulan,'' Disney has come up with a computer
program based on the hit animated film that should carry away your
kids. Like every other major animated film Disney has released in
recent years, the company has come out with an ``animated
storybook'' for ``Mulan.'' By David Bloom. 
. 
