</P>
<P>
   6. ASK MEN'S HEALTH. From Men's Health. Answers to questions on
sleeping pills, reheating food in the microwave and condoms.
(slugged: BC-RODALE-Q&AMP;A-NYTSF).
 &UR; -0- &QL;
</P>
