   TRAVEL-BRIEFS (Undated) _ Kool-Aid Week in Nebraska highlights
travel briefs.
</P>
<P>
   TRAVEL-Q&AMP;A (Undated) _ Beatles tours in England and Christmas on
Capri are subjects of travel questions. By Suzanne MacNeille.
</P>
<P>
   PRACTICAL-TRAVELER (Undated) _ Clothing optional cruises. By
Betsy Wade.
</P>
<P>
   CYBER-TRAVEL (Undated) _ Traveling the net: Finding ATM's abroad
and student air fares. By L.R. Shannon.
</P>
<P>
   TRAVEL-FLORIDA (Miami) _ Despite the fires, Florida tourism
rolls on. By Mireya Navarro.
</P>
