<HEADLINE>
ROMANTIC AND INTELLECTUAL PURSUITS
</HEADLINE>
  
 (Eds: This story also moved in the ``l'' lifestyle file)  
 By LEAH GARCHIK  
 c.1998 San Francisco Chronicle
<TEXT>
<P>
   J &UR; osh Brolin &LR; , 30-year-old actor and son of  &UR; James Brolin &LR; , is
dating  &UR; Pamela Anderson &LR; , reports New Weekly magazine _ and why
shouldn't an Australian magazine be an authority on this subject? _
which raises the prospect of  &UR; Barbra Streisand &LR;  becoming Anderson's
