<P>
   _ At last, the periodical you've been waiting for: Macauley's
Historical Essays. This volume, published in 1890, was checked out
of the North Beach Branch of the San Francisco library several days
before the great quake of April 18, 1906, kept out all these
years, &LR;  and returned, along with two others, during a recent
library-fine amnesty.
</P>
<P>
