<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1998-07-13 21:17 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A3141 &Cx1f; taf-z
u f &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-CENDANT-MARKETPLACE-N     07-13 1280
