<HEADLINE>
QUOTATION OF THE DAY
</HEADLINE>
 (Eds.: This quotation refers to BC-JAPAN-POLITICS-NYT, which moved
in ``i'' news file.) 
c.1998 N.Y. Times News Service   
<TEXT>
<P>
   ``Hashimoto is one of the best that the LDP can produce. Unless
someone terribly fresh and surprising comes along, it's hard to see
how the next prime minister can handle the issues head on and
fast.''
</P>
<P>
   _TAKASHI INOGUCHI, a political scientist at Tokyo University.
</P>
</TEXT>
