   GM-STRIKE (Flint, Mich.) _ It began 39 days ago as a simple
strike at a single GM factory over how modern-day workers should
build fenders and hoods. But like two neighborhood toughs daring
each other with escalating taunts, the dispute between GM and the
UAW union has grown so big, complicated and destructive that a
